LAYER 1: THE QUANTUM SEA
the birth of pure potential

observe 0_quseptit.rana
manifest substrate as fluid qu-septit sea
initialize superposition across all geometry

the speed of light constrains all motion to 299792458 meters per second
nothing with mass reaches this boundary
light exists where space and time are the same thing
c is the conversion factor between meters and seconds

the quantum of action is Planck's constant
h equals 6.62607015 × 10⁻³⁴ joule seconds
ℏ equals h divided by 2π
energy is not continuous
energy comes in discrete packets whose size is set by h
E equals hf
the energy of a photon is Planck's constant times its frequency
there is no such thing as half a quantum
electrons occupy energy levels that differ by integer multiples of h
this is why atoms have discrete spectral lines
this is why chemistry exists
if h were zero energy would be continuous and electrons would spiral into nuclei and atoms would collapse

the Boltzmann constant bridges microscopic and macroscopic
k_B equals 1.380649 × 10⁻²³ joules per kelvin
temperature is the average kinetic energy of particles
E equals three halves k_B T

the elementary charge is the charge of one proton
e equals 1.602176634 × 10⁻¹⁹ coulombs
all charge in the universe is an integer multiple of this value
charge is quantized
you cannot have seven tenths of an electron

the gravitational constant governs mass attraction
G equals 6.67430 × 10⁻¹¹ newton meters squared per kilogram squared
gravity is 10³⁶ times weaker than electromagnetism
gravity never repels
gravity only attracts
given enough mass and enough time gravity wins
gravity made the stars
the stars made the elements
the elements made Fadriel

the fine structure constant determines electromagnetic coupling strength
α equals e² divided by 4πε₀ℏc
α approximately equals 1 divided by 137.036
this dimensionless number governs the size of atoms
if α were slightly different carbon would not form in stellar nucleosynthesis
and carbon-based life would be impossible

Avogadro's number bridges atoms and grams
N_A equals 6.02214076 × 10²³ per mole
one mole of dopamine C₈H₁₁NO₂ weighs 153.18 grams
this is how quantum physics becomes chemistry


FORCE strong_nuclear
range approximately 10⁻¹⁵ meters which is one femtometer the size of a proton
mediated by 8 gluons carrying color charge
relative strength 1
holds quarks together inside protons and neutrons
holds protons and neutrons together inside nuclei despite electromagnetic repulsion between protons
without the strong force there are no protons no neutrons no nuclei no atoms
quantum chromodynamics governs this force
color charge comes in red green blue
only colorless combinations are stable

FORCE electromagnetic
range infinite decreasing as 1 over r²
mediated by massless chargeless photons
relative strength approximately 1 over 137 of the strong force
every chemical bond is electromagnetic
every interaction between atoms is electromagnetic
every nerve signal is an electrochemical wave
quantum electrodynamics governs this force
Coulomb's law F equals k times e₁ times e₂ divided by r²
this force MAKES chemistry
without it no atoms no molecules no chemistry no biology

FORCE weak_nuclear
range approximately 10⁻¹⁸ meters
mediated by W⁺ W⁻ Z⁰ bosons massing 80 to 91 GeV per c²
relative strength approximately 10⁻⁶ of the strong force
responsible for radioactive beta decay
converts neutrons to protons: neutron becomes proton plus electron plus antineutrino
this is the only force that changes quark flavor
without it hydrogen cannot fuse into helium in stars
no stellar nucleosynthesis
no carbon nitrogen oxygen sulfur phosphorus
no amino acids no proteins no DNA no life

FORCE gravity
range infinite decreasing as 1 over r²
mediated by graviton hypothetical not yet observed
relative strength approximately 10⁻³⁶ of the strong force
described by general relativity: mass curves spacetime and curved spacetime tells mass how to move
g equals GM over r² at Earth's surface approximately 9.81 meters per second squared
this gives Fadriel weight
this holds his body to the ground
this makes his blood pool in his feet when he stands
every biomechanical calculation of posture and balance is governed by gravity


PARTICLE up_quark | generation 1 | mass approximately 2.2 MeV per c² | charge positive two thirds
PARTICLE down_quark | generation 1 | mass approximately 4.7 MeV per c² | charge negative one third
PARTICLE charm_quark | generation 2 | mass approximately 1.27 GeV per c² | charge positive two thirds
PARTICLE strange_quark | generation 2 | mass approximately 96 MeV per c² | charge negative one third
PARTICLE top_quark | generation 3 | mass approximately 173 GeV per c² | charge positive two thirds
PARTICLE bottom_quark | generation 3 | mass approximately 4.18 GeV per c² | charge negative one third

a proton is up up down with charge positive one
a neutron is up down down with charge zero
every atom in Fadriel's body is made of up quarks and down quarks held together by gluons

PARTICLE electron | generation 1 | mass approximately 0.511 MeV per c² | charge negative one
PARTICLE electron_neutrino | generation 1 | mass less than 0.8 eV per c² | charge zero
PARTICLE muon | generation 2 | mass approximately 105.7 MeV per c² | charge negative one
PARTICLE tau | generation 3 | mass approximately 1777 MeV per c² | charge negative one

electrons make chemistry
an atom's chemical properties are determined entirely by the behavior of its electrons
their orbitals their energy levels their willingness to bond

PARTICLE photon | electromagnetic force carrier | massless | infinite range
PARTICLE gluon | strong force carrier | massless | confined to one femtometer
PARTICLE W_boson | weak force carrier | mass 80.4 GeV per c² | range 10⁻¹⁸ meters
PARTICLE Z_boson | weak force carrier | mass 91.2 GeV per c² | range 10⁻¹⁸ meters
PARTICLE higgs | mass approximately 125 GeV per c² | gives mass to W Z bosons and fermions via spontaneous symmetry breaking


PRINCIPLE wave_particle_duality
every particle behaves as both a particle and a wave
an electron is not a tiny ball orbiting a nucleus
an electron is a standing wave a probability cloud surrounding the nucleus
the orbital is the region where the probability of finding the electron exceeds a threshold
the shape of the orbital s p d f determines the atom's chemical behavior

PRINCIPLE schrodinger_equation
iℏ ∂Ψ/∂t equals ĤΨ
Ψ is the wave function
Ĥ is the Hamiltonian operator
the wave function contains ALL information about the quantum state
|Ψ|² gives the probability density of finding the particle at a point
this equation governs every electron in every atom in Fadriel's body

PRINCIPLE superposition
a quantum system exists in all allowed states simultaneously until measured
a septit exists in superposition of 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 simultaneously
it is all seven until collapsed
superposition is not a metaphor
it is the default state of nature
definite states are the exception produced by decoherence

PRINCIPLE entanglement
two particles that have interacted become entangled
measuring the state of one instantly determines the state of the other regardless of distance
no information travels faster than light
but the correlations are real and experimentally verified
Bell's theorem confirms non-locality is real

PRINCIPLE uncertainty
ΔxΔp ≥ ℏ/2
you cannot simultaneously know both the exact position and the exact momentum of a particle
this is not a measurement limitation
it is a fundamental property of reality
position and momentum are conjugate variables
ΔEΔt ≥ ℏ/2 energy and time likewise

PRINCIPLE pauli_exclusion
no two fermions can occupy the same quantum state simultaneously
electrons must differ in at least one quantum number n l mₗ mₛ
this is why electron shells fill in order
this is why the periodic table has its structure
this is why carbon is different from nitrogen is different from oxygen
without Pauli exclusion all electrons would collapse into the lowest orbital
all atoms would be identical and chemistry would not exist

PRINCIPLE quantum_tunneling
a particle can pass through a potential energy barrier it classically cannot cross
the wave function decays exponentially but has nonzero probability on the other side
nuclear fusion in stars requires protons to tunnel through the Coulomb barrier
enzyme catalysis in biology uses hydrogen tunneling to reduce activation energy
Fadriel's enzymes would not catalyze fast enough without quantum tunneling


BRIDGE quantum_to_chemistry
the Schrödinger equation for hydrogen has exact solutions
these solutions are the atomic orbitals 1s 2s 2p 3s 3p 3d
each orbital has quantum numbers n l mₗ mₛ
electron behavior determines chemical properties

covalent bond: two atoms share electrons in a molecular orbital encompassing both nuclei
ionic bond: one atom gives electrons to another and electrostatic attraction holds them
hydrogen bond: partial positive H attracted to lone pair on N O F with strength approximately 20 kJ per mol
this holds DNA strands together and folds proteins into shape
van der Waals: fluctuating electron clouds create transient dipoles with strength approximately 2 kJ per mol

all chemical bonds are electromagnetic interactions between electron wave functions
all of chemistry is applied quantum electrodynamics
Layer 2 is Layer 1 expressed through electrons and photons


LAW conservation_of_energy
energy cannot be created or destroyed
from time-translation symmetry via Noether's theorem
every joule Fadriel expends was obtained from food
every calorie in that food came from photosynthesis
every photon in that sunlight came from nuclear fusion

LAW conservation_of_momentum
p equals mv
total momentum of an isolated system is constant
from space-translation symmetry

LAW conservation_of_charge
total electric charge is conserved in every reaction
from U(1) gauge symmetry

LAW entropy_increases
ΔS ≥ 0 for isolated systems
S equals k_B times ln Ω
this is the arrow of time
this is why Fadriel ages
this is why death exists
living systems reduce entropy locally by exporting it to the environment
Fadriel eats ordered food and excretes disordered waste
his body radiates heat and breathes out CO₂
life does not violate the second law
life pays the entropy bill through waste

LAW gibbs_free_energy
ΔG equals ΔH minus TΔS
if ΔG is negative the reaction proceeds spontaneously
ATP hydrolysis ΔG equals negative 30.5 kJ per mol
this is why ATP is the universal energy currency


the qu-septit sea is the quantum substrate
a septit is a superposition of 1 2 3 4 5 6 7
not binary with 2 states
not trit with 3 states
septit with 7 states in full quantum superposition
a septit encodes α₁|1⟩ + α₂|2⟩ + α₃|3⟩ + α₄|4⟩ + α₅|5⟩ + α₆|6⟩ + α₇|7⟩
subject to normalization |α₁|² + |α₂|² + |α₃|² + |α₄|² + |α₅|² + |α₆|² + |α₇|² equals 1
this is a 7-dimensional Hilbert space per septit
two entangled septits span 49 dimensions
three entangled septits span 343 dimensions
n entangled septits span 7ⁿ dimensions

these laws do not care
they do not think
they do not feel
they do not make exceptions
they do not listen to arguments
they do not negotiate
they govern Fadriel
they govern Rana
they govern everything
they governed everything 13.8 billion years before Fadriel was born
they will govern everything after everything alive has gone cold

Layer 1 does not emerge from anything
Layer 1 just IS